{
  "os": "cisco_nxos",
  "command": "show bgp vrf all all",
  "schema": {
    "name": "ShowIpBgpResult",
    "fields": {
      "vrfs": {
        "type": {
          "type": "dict",
          "key": "str",
          "value": {
            "name": "VrfEntry",
            "fields": {
              "address_families": {
                "type": {
                  "type": "dict",
                  "key": "str",
                  "value": {
                    "name": "AddressFamilyEntry",
                    "fields": {
                      "table_version": {
                        "type": "int",
                        "required": true
                      },
                      "router_id": {
                        "type": "str",
                        "required": true
                      },
                      "routes": {
                        "type": {
                          "type": "dict",
                          "key": "str",
                          "value": {
                            "name": "RouteEntry",
                            "fields": {
                              "paths": {
                                "type": {
                                  "type": "list",
                                  "items": {
                                    "name": "PathEntry",
                                    "fields": {
                                      "status_codes": {
                                        "type": "str",
                                        "required": false
                                      },
                                      "path_type": {
                                        "type": "str",
                                        "required": false
                                      },
                                      "next_hop": {
                                        "type": "str",
                                        "required": true
                                      },
                                      "metric": {
                                        "type": "int",
                                        "required": false
                                      },
                                      "locprf": {
                                        "type": "int",
                                        "required": false
                                      },
                                      "weight": {
                                        "type": "int",
                                        "required": true
                                      },
                                      "as_path": {
                                        "type": "str",
                                        "required": false
                                      },
                                      "origin": {
                                        "type": "str",
                                        "required": true
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                },
                                "required": true
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        },
                        "required": false
                      },
                      "route_distinguishers": {
                        "type": {
                          "type": "dict",
                          "key": "str",
                          "value": {
                            "name": "RouteDistinguisherEntry",
                            "fields": {
                              "rd_vrf": {
                                "type": "str",
                                "required": false
                              },
                              "routes": {
                                "type": {
                                  "type": "dict",
                                  "key": "str",
                                  "value": {
                                    "type": "ref",
                                    "name": "RouteEntry"
                                  }
                                },
                                "required": true
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        },
                        "required": false
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                "required": true
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "required": true
      }
    }
  },
  "examples": [
    {
      "name": "Multiple VRFs with IPv4/IPv6 unicast and VPNv4/VPNv6 with route distinguishers",
      "input": "BGP routing table information for VRF default, address family IPv4 Unicast\nBGP table version is 100, local router ID is 10.10.0.1\nStatus: s-suppressed, x-deleted, S-stale, d-dampened, h-history, *-valid, >-best\nPath type: i-internal, e-external, c-confed, l-local, a-aggregate, r-redist, I-injected\nOrigin codes: i - IGP, e - EGP, ? - incomplete, | - multipath, & - backup\n\n   Network            Next Hop            Metric     LocPrf     Weight Path\n*>l10.10.0.1/32       0.0.0.0                           100      32768 i\n*>e10.10.0.2/32       10.10.2.1                                      0 64102 64002 i\n*>r10.16.1.0/24       0.0.0.0               4444        100      32768 ?\n\nBGP routing table information for VRF PROD, address family IPv4 Unicast\nBGP table version is 55, local router ID is 192.168.1.1\nStatus: s-suppressed, x-deleted, S-stale, d-dampened, h-history, *-valid, >-best\nPath type: i-internal, e-external, c-confed, l-local, a-aggregate, r-redist, I-injected\nOrigin codes: i - IGP, e - EGP, ? - incomplete, | - multipath, & - backup\n\n   Network            Next Hop            Metric     LocPrf     Weight Path\n*>i172.16.0.0/16      10.0.0.2                 0        100          0 65001 i\n*>r192.168.1.0/24     0.0.0.0                  0        100      32768 ?\n\nBGP routing table information for VRF default, address family VPNv4 Unicast\nBGP table version is 200, local router ID is 10.10.0.1\nStatus: s-suppressed, x-deleted, S-stale, d-dampened, h-history, *-valid, >-best\nPath type: i-internal, e-external, c-confed, l-local, a-aggregate, r-redist, I-injected\nOrigin codes: i - IGP, e - EGP, ? - incomplete, | - multipath, & - backup\n\n   Network            Next Hop            Metric     LocPrf     Weight Path\nRoute Distinguisher: 65000:100     (VRF PROD)\n*>i172.16.0.0/16      10.0.0.2                 0        100          0 65001 i\n*>r192.168.1.0/24     0.0.0.0                  0        100      32768 ?\n",
